{"tid":641529,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【北韓大車禍】左派網「烏有之鄉」組旅團32死 孔慶東：心情格外悲痛！","createTime":"2018-04-25T05:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-25T13:48:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":74,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"c7481be297b4f0c11ab7d9a39a1c6b6a3ccd800e","tid":641529,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T05:24:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180425/large/1524631191_9971.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180425%2Flarge%2F1524631191_9971.jpg&h=f014e9ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180425/large/1524631193_e7f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180425%2Flarge%2F1524631193_e7f8.jpg&h=86436dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北韓周日發生牽涉中國遊客的大車禍，造成32名中國遊客死亡。網上陸續有消息指，這次旅行團疑似北京左派網站「烏有之鄉」旗下星火旅遊網主辦，該團早於3月已宣傳這次北韓觀光團，據報遇難者名單中，可能包括星火旅遊刁姓負責人。《蘋果》今日嘗試聯絡星火旅遊客服及負責人，但電話已關機，暫未有人回應。<br />\n<br />\n曾口出狂言指「香港人是狗」北京大學中文系教授孔慶東，今日在微博留言致哀：「一夜沒有睡好。大前天在朝鮮（北韓）黃海北道遇難的，已經證實為星火旅遊團。多位遇難團友給我托（託）夢，心情格外悲痛！」<br />\n<br />\n另一名網民「秀才先生」則寫道：「烏有之鄉星火紅色旅行團......我的好朋友刁偉銘（烏有之鄉網站主編）等同志的赴朝旅遊團遇難......沉痛悼念刁偉銘同志和所有遇難同胞！願他們在天堂一路走好。」<br />\n<br />\n根據網上紀錄，星火旅遊網於上月9日宣傳「星火旅遊赴朝鮮紅色之旅：紀念抗美援朝戰爭勝利65周年」，於本月18至24日成行，團費為5,990元人民幣（約7,567港元），限客30人。「參加者將在（遼寧）丹東火車站集合乘坐國際列車前往朝鮮（北韓），期間參觀平壤、南浦、開城、檜倉郡、元山、上甘嶺地區、金剛山特區等7大城市與地區。」<br />\n<br />\n奪命車禍發生於周日下午6時許，一輛載有34名中國遊客的旅遊巴，從北韓黃海北道一處大橋墮下，造成32人死亡，2人重傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180425/58115722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180425%2F58115722&d=i%2FJsSzWykDEOeH%2BadX%2B7WpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=ea953298\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180425%2F58115722&h=7b19dc5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180425/58115722</a>"},{"pid":"8587fb13f7b77b5853c97972bc4d912250f777d3","tid":641529,"uid":163350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T05:26:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71ed698a01a17f19d4c0c749ea72e944eb51b881","tid":641529,"uid":17103,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T05:35:22.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》今日嘗試聯絡星火旅遊客服及負責人，但電話已關機，暫未有人回應。<br />\n<br />\n死撚左重點應"},{"pid":"c097074475d014c293a6afbc8bbe4f0517c36885","tid":641529,"uid":49392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"天乜撚堂，支那人思想係人死如燈滅囉"},{"pid":"777225626008ddd40eece41ad37fdb2156a5611e","tid":641529,"uid":2974,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T05:53:24.000Z","msg":"孔慶東是狗，屌你老母臭閪，快撚d落埋去陪你d同胞"},{"pid":"25287a95d8e2d3bd3218f1decf3dcecfa88ea1d3","tid":641529,"uid":25424,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T05:54:17.000Z","msg":"紀念抗美援朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲唔成堆枉死陰魂攪你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e8c26a38c27b592ccf8ce4a1a61f0d80f4a81f","tid":641529,"uid":6799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"25287a95d8e2d3bd3218f1decf3dcecfa88ea1d3","tid":641529,"uid":25424,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T05:54:17.000Z","msg":"紀念抗美援朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲唔成堆枉死陰魂攪你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.